### 4.2. Tentar agendar num DOMINGO (Erro 422 - Validador)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/consultas
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {COLOQUE_SEU_TOKEN_AQUI}

{
  "medicoId": "55434eb1-8db6-4c1b-b6c7-a803f3808815",
  "gestanteId": "cd0cba67-e0e8-4679-8192-a2b0077bf81d",
